   299	The `setInboundHandler()` method from earlier drafts is replaced by the standard `onMessage()` / `offMessage()` contract from `RelayInboundAdapter`. Products wire the registry during initialization:
   300	
   301	```typescript
   302	const runtime = createAssistant(definition, {
