    80	| WF-2: Handle inbound message via dispatch | `core` | WF-1 | Exercises `dispatch()`, capability table, hooks, `emit()`; `InboundMessage` requires `userId` per Contradiction 2 resolution |
    81	| WF-3: Create and manage sessions | `sessions` | sessions spec | Parallel with WF-1; requires in-memory adapter |
